@1433  = ~I'm Lysan, the barmaid. If I may be of service to you, you need but ask.~
@1434  = ~What do you do here, Lysan?~
@1435  = ~I would like to ask you some more questions.~
@1436  = ~Farewell for now.~
@1437  = ~As I said, I'm a barmaid. I help take care of the customers. I serve food and drinks, chat with folks, and listen to what they have to say. You learn a lot if you take the time to listen.~
@1438  = ~Have you heard any rumors you can share with me?~
@1439  = ~[no text]~
@1440  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1441  = ~Well... I hear tales. Folks have been talking about the recent avalanche, the haunted vale, missing folks, monsters, and Arundel.~
@1442  = ~What are they saying about the avalanche?~
@1443  = ~A haunted vale? That sounds interesting.~
@1444  = ~Who or what is Arundel?~
@1445  = ~You say people are missing?~
@1446  = ~Are monsters a problem here?~
@1447  = ~Let me ask you something else.~
@1448  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1449  = ~I hear it was a bad one. The pass out of the valley's been blocked and won't be open again until... who knows when? Some folks are trapped here and none too happy about it. Not much that can be done though, just wait for spring and see if it clears enough for travel.~
@1450  = ~You mentioned a haunted vale. Can you tell me about it?~
