@1453  = ~You said something about monsters. Are they a problem here?~
@1454  = ~[no text]~
@1455  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1456  = ~Most folks call it the Vale of Shadows. It's always dark there, like twilight or a moonlit night. Anyway, there are those who say spirits of the dead wander the vale. Folks don't go there anymore. They're afraid to. Maybe someone should do something about that...~
@1457  = ~You spoke of the avalanche. What can you tell me about it?~
