@1461  = ~[no text]~
@1462  = ~[no text]~
@1463  = ~I will take my leave of you now. Farewell.~
@1464  = ~Arundel... he's the local sage or hermit. I don't know rightly what to call him. Folks have a lot of respect for him though. Anyway, I guess he's taken an interest in a lot of the goings on around here of late. He's been seen out and about more than is usual for him. That's all I know.~
@1465  = ~Earlier you mentioned an avalanche. Can you tell me about it?~
@1466  = ~I would like to hear more about the haunted vale you spoke of.~
@1467  = ~Did you say something about missing people earlier?~
@1468  = ~I believe you said monsters were of concern. Are they a problem here?~
@1469  = ~Aye, folks have been vanishing without a trace... I recall something about a man's wife gone missing. He packed up and left his home and all to go find her. Another is the smithy's young son. You might want to talk to him if you have an interest.~
@1470  = ~[no text]~
