@1522  = ~[no text]~
@1523  = ~Very well, I shall leave. Farewell.~
@1524  = ~Hmm... I am somewhat familiar with Auril. The Frostmaiden is not very popular among most peoples. Many worship her out of fear rather than love or devotion. Her truly faithful are rare and secretive, to say the least. Why do you seek such a person?~
@1525  = ~I have questions regarding the faith.~
