@1663  = ~Yes... so I did... The truth of the matter is that I do not know who is responsible. I can only assure you that it is not I, nor is it anyone in this vale. Were it to be otherwise, I would sense it.~ [KRES_31]
@1664  = ~That is not the answer I was promised, spirit.~
@1665  = ~Then be about your task! I have nothing to say to you until it is completed! Fare thee well.~ [KRES_32]
@1666  = ~Farewell.~
@1667  = ~You have done me a great service by removing the threat of the Aurilite priestess. For that, I am grateful... However, I would ask you to leave me to my rest now. There is nothing else that either of us can do for the other. Farewell.~
@1668  = ~Farewell.~
