@1815  = ~Well, I've heard tell of raiders—goblins and the like—*never* seen in the Pass before. Folks, travelers, have gone missing, and no one knows where. Lots of strange goings-on, got a lot of folks worried. You might want to speak to Arundel—if his beard's any sign, he's got a lot of knowing to his years. You can find him at the base of the great tree—his is the two-storied house to the south and west.~
