@2025  = ~We showed Aldwin Eidan's signet ring that we had found upstairs, and he confessed to having forged the claim to the Evening Shade... with enough pressure, he eventually agreed that he would go confess his crime to the elders of Kuldahar and face whatever punishment they see fit to give him.~
@2026  = ~Why did you steal the Heartstone Gem?~
@2027  = ~So... what is this battle all about, anyway?~
@2028  = ~We spoke with Sister Calliana, the acting head priest of the Temple of Ilmater in Kuldahar. She's assumed the role of head priest of the temple ever since Mother Egenia vanished a few weeks ago. Calliana also mentioned that another member of the Ilmater clergy, a man by the name of Brother Poquelin, passed through Kuldahar recently from all the way from Cormyr and was going to try and get help from the Monastery of the Weeping Lilac in Bryn Shander. Calliana fears he may have been abducted as well.~
@2029  = ~Is that why you need the Heartstone Gem?~
@2030  = ~Who, or what, are you?~
@2031  = ~Uh... what are you talking about? You are really strange.~
@2032  = ~Is that why you need the Heartstone Gem?~
@2033  = ~Who is this "old friend"? It sounds like you have a grudge with him.~
@2034  = ~Whatever. Just hand over the Heartstone Gem and I'll be on my way.~
@2035  = ~Then why do you need the Heartstone Gem?~
@2036  = ~Uh...~
@2037  = ~I'll break you into pieces, little one.~
