@3191  = ~Gerth was going on about one of the tombs said to be in the Vale of Shadows—says one of them's the tomb of Kresselack the Black Wolf. Terrorized this region years ago, he did, with a whole legion of soldiers, shamans and priests under his banner. Rumor has it he has a sword as large as a man, able to cleave enemies in half; the sword carried some enchantment that helped ward off the cold... but not the chill of death, I'll wager.~
