@4322  = ~I encountered an undead creation today that was used as the "eyes and mouth" of a necromancer. I sensed no evil in it, so I demanded that the coward controlling the proxy face me. From this, I learned that the necromancer was a worshipper of Talona, that disgusting goddess of poison and disease.~
@4323  = ~[no text]~
@4324  = ~I met Yxunomei in the heart of Dragon's Eye. She was surprised that I was there, interfering with her "vendetta." I had no desire to mince words with her, so I told her I was going to rip the Heartstone Gem from her cold, dead, scaly hands. She promptly attacked me.~
@4325  = ~[YESLICK 37] Your ego is positively elven. Drop it a notch, lest I do it for you.~ [YESLK37]
