@4407  = ~Up until a few weeks ago, Revered Mother Egenia presided over this house. Alas, she, like so many others in town, has gone missing and is presumed dead. Being the next highest-ranking member of the clergy, I have assumed the duties of the head of this temple until either she or Revered Brother Poquelin returns.~
