@4415  = ~Evil has cast its shadow upon this land; even the weather seems to have been affected by its presence. The source of this evil is unknown to me, but its touch can be felt everywhere. Several townspeople have mysteriously disappeared, including our former head priest, Revered Mother Egenia. Being the next highest-ranking member of the clergy, I have assumed the duties of the head of this temple until either she or Revered Brother Poquelin returns.~
