@5019  = ~~
@5020  = ~Great, two identical, sniveling servants of a pathetic god... just what this world needs.~
@5021  = ~Of course. What services in particular do you seek?~
@5022  = ~I am in need of a healer.~
@5023  = ~I am in need of a place to rest for the night.~
@5024  = ~I could use a drink.~
@5025  = ~I'm looking to purchase weapons and equipment.~
@5026  = ~~
