@5393  = ~[YESLICK 39]~ [YESLK39]
@5394  = ~::There is no truth I can offer in these broken words that will show you that I nor this gift mean Jho-nyn harm.::~
@5395  = ~[IMOEN 12]~ [IMOEN12]
@5396  = ~[IMOEN 13]~ [IMOEN13]
@5397  = ~Words may not suffice to show me your intentions, but a song might. Teach me your song, Elisia, and I shall see to it the blade you hold is carried safely to its rightful owner.~
