@6270  = ~Oh my god... I remember... I remember killing my own child! What have I done?~
@6271  = ~Whew! That was close. I almost got turned into one of those snake thingies.~
@6272  = ~How in the Nine Hells do I get out of this place?~
@6273  = ~Thank Ilmater I got through that all right.~
@6274  = ~Snakes. Snakes. Snakes.~
@6275  = ~Thank you for delivering us from the spell of these evil creatures.~
@6276  = ~Thank you for delivering us from the spell of these evil creatures. I guess it was hard to not kill... some of us to get to him...~
