@6292  = ~Your brother? Where is he?~
@6293  = ~Silas didn't make it. The largest yeti I've ever seen tore out of the snow and took a piece out of him with its claws. He fell, dead as a stone, blood everywhere. There... there was nothing I could do. He was carrying our family heirloom... but it's lost to us now.~
