@6303  = ~Thank you. Now that Silas is gone, that heirloom is all I have left to remember my family by. I would appreciate its safe return. Also, if you come across any more yetis, you might want to collect their pelts once you've done away with the beasts. Conlan, the blacksmith here in town, buys the pelts for a fair price.~
