@9250  = ~May I ask you some questions?~
@9251  = ~Not at this time. Farewell.~
@9252  = ~Greetings. It's good to see you again. What can I help you with?~
@9253  = ~Our god is kind and forgiving. We are not. As servants of Ilmater, it is our duty to strip all resistance to suffering from the bodies of believers and unbelievers alike. Once your resistance has been stripped away, you will weep in the arms of Ilmater.~
