@9303  = ~From what I can gather he is the dwarven god of scholars, inventors, and explorers. He's not well known and frowned upon by some of the other gods. They consider him to be a bit... whimsical, I guess you'd say. Anyway, Dugmaren felt that the dwarves should get out and explore the world more.~
