@9308  = ~A brilliant architect known as Alkonos the Visionary built this complex. He was a devout follower of Dugmaren and took offense that his deity had no formal temple. So, he petitioned the king and was granted permission to construct one. During the construction he became known as Alkonos the Mad.~
