@10505 = ~Saablic Tan always thought *he* was the master of magic. Always turning me away, always sending his precious, stinking orogs after my little umber hulks, training them to kill my pets on sight! I had the last laugh, though, when I turned *him* into an umber hulk and placed him among his twisted creations.~
