@10522 = ~Fine, fine. I'll do it. Are you happy now?~
@10523 = ~No, not really. I just like using morality against people. I also like watching these worms die. Why not combine the two? It's fun for everyone. Well, maybe just for me. I don't know. I haven't been out of here much recently. Why should I? Ha ha! I can see everything from here! I AM ALWAYS WATCHING, WATCHING!~
