@10751 = ~Don't be an idiot. Quit trying to find trouble or you'll get more than you bargained for.~
@10752 = ~Fair enough. Let's get down to business, then. What are you doing down here?~
@10753 = ~I don't find trouble. I *make* trouble. Today, I've decided to make trouble with you. What are you going to do about it, little miss?~
@10754 = ~You know it. We are a painfully small minority down here.~
