@10814 = ~I don't know. I'm not sure I want to know, either. Every once in a while, when Marketh comes here, I have the urge to jump up and hit him. I thought about doing the same thing when Poquelin came here. As soon as I did, he grabbed my face and looked right into my eyes. It was like he knew.~
