@15352 = ~As I watched what I thought was our salvation enter every crevice of the Hand, I became horrified. Something had gone terribly wrong! The force that was supposed to bring life to the land began to twist and corrupt it. It was draining everything and everyone within the Hand... of its soul.~ [LARR_42]
