@15870 = ~Redemption? I have no desire for redemption. I now possess all that I have dreamed of. Guilt is but a small price to pay for such power. I'll not stand here and be judged by you! You are nothing! You are but an insect that I shall squash beneath my boot! Sentries! Slay them!~
@15871 = ~Pomab? What in the Nine Hells are you doing here?~
