@16416 = ~The boy was just the first. Several nights later, another disappeared—Maegan Potts, the local midwife. Her husband Kaleel was grief-stricken to the point of madness. With barely a word to anyone, he snatched up his sword and marched off into the darkness after his wife. No one has heard from him since.~ [ARUN_18]
@16417 = ~And now, the abductions are occurring *more* frequently. Eidan, the old innkeeper from the Evening Shade, was taken only three days ago.~ [ARUN_19]
