@18351 = ~~
@18352 = ~I want to thank you for finding my boy for me. I had almost given up hope. I nearly fell out of my chair when he came bouncing through the door, telling tales of heroes and monsters with nary a scratch on him. He's in the back now resting. Go on in and say hello if you wish.~
