@19453 = ~Unlike the rest of my people, Malavon wanted to join with the Revered Brother. I discovered this, so he abducted me and took me to Marketh for "safekeeping." They eventually found out anyway. Now Poquelin is planning some sort of assault on my former home. And I... I am left here with Marketh.~
