@19455 = ~If you want to break up Poquelin's army, you'll need each of the lieutenant's badges. Marketh has one. They open an invisible barrier at the back of the fallen temple. Brother Perdiem and his undead fellows watch over it. Whatever you need to do, please... don't hurt Marketh. It's not his fault that he does bad things...~
