@21613 = ~Quost's Staff of the Elements +4~
@21614 = ~The wizard Quost Curion was the creator of this staff. He was a mercenary mage who loved summoning allies to dole out punishment against his enemies. Often, however, he found that he was running out of spells at a time when he needed them the most. At great personal expense, Quost created this staff over a period of seven years. His staff was very effective until he went into battle with an abjurer who was prepared to deal with his summoned monsters. Quost was killed in battle in 1063, and his staff was claimed by his killer, Balder Renold.

