@21616 = ~This unique brass ring is set with mandrake root instead of a precious stone. It was created by the druid Eimhec of Silvanus to protect his underlings on their travels. It was first worn by Omad the Wise before he became an archdruid. It was later worn by Jontan Dunmoss, who was killed in a fen by Malarite marauders. The ring fell into their hands for several years before its new owner, Hunter Renard, was shot dead by elven rangers in northern woods.

