@21702 = ~Are you any relation to Old Jed, the fisherman from Easthaven?~
@21703 = ~I row boats out in the great Maer Dualdon. I keeps me *eye* open for rocks and ice under the water. Some say I be the best sailor in Icewind Dale since... since me old Uncle Jed.~
@21704 = ~That's a nice boat you're working on.~
