@21794 = ~~
@21795 = ~~
@21796 = ~~
@21797 = ~Icewind Dale is one of the most remote areas in Faerûn. I felt it was my challenge and duty to bring trade and commerce to this desolate place. I see a golden future in these icy wastes.~
@21798 = ~~
@21799 = ~~
