@21877 = ~Help! Help me, please... my brother and I were playing, and he fell down the well! I think he's hurt!~
@21878 = ~Hnnn...? Well, now... aren't *you* a sight for tired eyes... a new face in Lonelywood, and such a *handsome* one, too. What's your name?~
