@22956 = ~~
@22957 = ~~
@22958 = ~He raises his axe an' swings at me. Almost had me, too. He was so fast with the blade... I barely raised me shield in time to block the blow. Last thing I remember was me shield shatterin' an' me fallin' from the bluff.~
