@23658 = ~I welcome you, humbly, in the knowledge we have wronged you. I am Jorn, shaman of the Bear Tribe. Please accept our apologies.~
@23659 = ~In life, Wylfdene was my friend and cousin. He was a truly noble man. Stubborn and proud at times, but never like that... thing that sat among us. I was a fool for believing he was my kin.~
@23660 = ~I am blood of his blood. I should have known. I suspected at first, but I was so proud to see all of our people gathered... all for one cause. We were united, at last. I was blinded by pride.~
