@24549 = ~~
@24550 = ~Aye, me business here is me own, stranger. But ye've found me, ye have. If ye want, ye can tell the fellows down in the Sunset Mountains I'm well an' good, making trouble as always. Now who are ye an' what do ye want?~
@24551 = ~~
