@26009 = ~We fought off a creature that was stalking the streets at night. We believe it was a werewolf, and that it is the one behind the murders in town.~
@26010 = ~We spoke with Kieran about the enchanted blade Doogal purchased. He seems to think that it may be a werewolf that's doing all the killing in town.~
@26011 = ~We talked to Doogal about Dolan's murder. He told us that he witnessed the attack and tried to save his brother, but his dagger had no effect on the beast.~
@26012 = ~No, but can we see what you have for sale?~
@26013 = ~Nothing yet. Farewell.~
@26014 = ~Why would he want to talk to Kieran about buying a magic weapon?~
@26015 = ~Do you think Doogal is planning to go after the beast himself?~
