@26020 = ~How do you know the creature that attacked you *wasn't* a werewolf?~
@26021 = ~Perhaps it did. Tell me, what can you recall of the past few nights?~
@26022 = ~Calm yourself. Surely there must be something we can do to help?~
@26023 = ~You're a murdering monster... that's what you've become. Now it's time to pay for your evil deeds!~
@26024 = ~Don't worry, your suffering shall soon be over. Hold still... this will only hurt for a moment.~
@26025 = ~Tough luck, eh? Oh well... as long as you keep your distance from us, I really don't care what you do at night. Farewell.~
@26026 = ~Very well. But if we discover a way to remove your curse, we'll be back.~
@26027 = ~Kieran gave us this magic amulet. Take it... as long as you wear it, it will prevent you from changing into a werewolf.~
@26028 = ~You're welcome, Emmerich. Farewell.~
