@26639 = ~Don't know if you've been to the temple of Waukeen in town—I always stop by to drop a few coins in to give my business a little boost.~
@26640 = ~Don't stray too far into the woods; there are things worse than bears and wolves in the shadows of the Lonely Wood.~
@26641 = ~I hear an expedition to scout out the barbarian camp by the dwarves ended in disaster. The only survivor, Roald Tunnelfist, is still in town, but I don't know for how much longer.~
