@26862 = ~The character will fight like a defensive fighter, save that, when done with a target, he will move to the member of the party with the lowest current Hit Points. If the character has healing spells or Lay On Hands available, he will use one of them on the wounded character. The character then chooses the nearest target and attacks.
~
