@32120 = ~Grand Master (5 slots): The character receives +3 to hit, +5 to damage, -3 to Speed Factor, and (for warriors only) an extra attack per round with the selected weapon. This extra attack is in addition to the bonus already provided by weapon specialization, so a 9th-level Fighter with Grand Mastery would attack 3 times per round.~
