@34182 = ~We met with Gaspar the Fishmonger in Easthaven. He told us of a trade he'd arranged with a merchant in Caer-Dineval. The caravan hasn't arrived yet, but it should be arriving any day now. It sounds like the town really needs the supplies the caravan is bringing.~
@34183 = ~We met with Gaspar the Fishmonger in Easthaven. He told us of a trade he'd arranged with a merchant in Caer-Dineval. The caravan hasn't arrived yet, but it should be arriving any day now. I wonder if it's the caravan that Hrothgar asked us to find.~
