@34188 = ~We found Old Jed, drunk, in the cellar of the Winter's Cradle. He told us that Everard and the other villagers had been captured by giants and were being held in a stockade south of the town, past the bridge. As soon as we were done talking to him, he passed out.~
@34189 = ~We convinced Old Jed, one of the local Easthaven fishermen, that he's caught in a self-destructive cycle of alcohol abuse. He should lay off the alcohol from now on... or at least drink a little less.~
