@35217 = ~The creature stares with open derision, sticking out its forked tongue rudely. It scoots off to <FAMILIAR_SUMMONER>. Obviously, it doesn't want to talk to you...~
@35218 = ~The impish creature regards you suspiciously, wary of a kick or slap headed its way, before sidling a step or two closer. "Yeah, boss? You want something?"~
@35219 = ~"Oh, sure. Stick me in your smelly pack. Ever thought of putting some mint in there? Baaah..." Reluctantly, the imp crawls into your pack.~
@35220 = ~It seems disgusted as you pat it on the head. "Oh, now I'm a cute little bunny? Give me a break, boss." The imp darts away and does a heebie-jeebie dance.~
@35221 = ~It looks at you incredulously, wondering if you are serious or if this is a prelude to a slap. "You want *me* to give *you* advice, boss? That's a first."~
@35222 = ~The demon curses under its breath briefly. "Boss, that caravan may be our best bet to score some easy gold."~
@35223 = ~It looks around a few moments before turning back to you. "Yeah, I got advice. Get your tail outta here, or hadn't you figured that out? Sheesh, ye're dumb."~
@35224 = ~It rolls its eyes in an exaggerated fashion. "What? Now I'm your tourist guide? Do whatever you want, boss. Go kill a king or something, sheesh."~
@35225 = ~"Do whatever you want, boss, but there's something big going down here."~
@35226 = ~"Let's see... advice. Advice... advice. Oh, yeah, I know... STOP BUGGIN' ME! Yeah, that's the ticket..."~
@35227 = ~The demon looks about. "What? Seems like a cheery enough place. Slaughter the locals, set yourself up as absolute ruler and tyrant. Works for me."~
@35228 = ~"But you want my advice? I'd say you're screwed, boss. But that's just my opinion. You can go ahead and do whatever you want."~
@35229 = ~It gives looks about and gives a quick shiver. "Yeah, I got advice right, boss. Stick your head between your legs an' kiss your butt goodbye."~
@35230 = ~It looks at you suspiciously, its sulfur eyes squinting. "Hmph. Since when are you so interested in me, boss? Up 'til now, it's all been you, you, you."~
@35231 = ~"But if you're really concerned, you could get me some healing. I got scratches, you know... you wouldn't want me to die, would you? I'm too useful!"~
@35232 = ~"But since you're asking, I could use healing. Ichor's running bad... you wouldn't want to send me back to the planes, would you? *That* would be a shame..."~
@35233 = ~"But, hmmm, let me see. I'm kinda hungry. How about a puppy sandwich? A steak? A chicken sacrifice? C'mon, throw me a bone here, sheesh!"~
@35234 = ~"But since you asked, I think you should get more gold. I wanna sleep in a BIG bag of gold. I could swim in it... yeah, that's it, swim in the gold... yeah..."~
@35235 = ~"But I would like to say that you run around too much. Here, there, back again... sheesh! Don't you ever stop awhile, set up shop? Gimme a break, boss!"~
@35236 = ~"But since you asked, I wanna register a complaint. Where's all *my* magical stuff? I want a big sword... and a bag of holding... and some wands, yeah, wands..."~
@35237 = ~It looks ahead and sighs, scratching its rear luridly. "Oh, sure. Only, what, another fifty years of wanderin' around? Don't you ever settle down? Sheesh..."~
@35238 = ~The imp reels from the blow. "HeeEEYY! Cripes! What wuz that for?! I did everything you told me to, boss! Sheesh! Some people..."~
@35239 = ~Another slap sends it to the floor, frantically covering its head. "Gaaah! Okay! You're the boss-<MANWOMAN>! YOU boss, ME just little follower! I get it!"~
@35240 = ~"Ow! Dammit, stop it! I'll do whatever you say, just stop slappin'!" It takes steps away, muttering something about "abusive codependent relationships" or similar.~
@35241 = ~The imp darts away at the last second. "Nyah! Thhhppppfffttt! You couldn't hit the broad side of a barn! You suck!" It dashes away before a reprisal can come.~
@35242 = ~It rolls its eyes. "Oh, sure. Stick me in your smelly pack. Ever thought of sticking some mint in there? Baaah..." It reluctantly crawls in.~
