@39443 = ~This hammer—not to be confused with the elven made Dwarf Thrower—is only usable by dwarves. In the capable hands of a dwarven warrior, the hammer may be thrown at an opponent. The magic in the hammer draws it back to the hand of its wielder. If it hits an opponent, it does double the normal damage that a hammer would normally do. Against giants and ogres, the hammer does an additional +8 damage due to the special hatred that dwarves hold against these races.

STATISTICS:

Combat abilities:
– Returns to the wielder's hand when thrown

