@39449 = ~This ancient bronze sword is set with six matching bloodstones and was apparently forged for Azoun the First, a long-dead king of Cormyr. It saw little use and eventually found its way to a favored of the king's guards. Despite the aid of its illusionary magic, that unnamed soldier fell in a later battle, and the sword was lost to brigands or scavengers.

