 11 Strength

Weight: 7~
@39460 = ~The benefits inherent in this sword are plain to see: It is exceptionally accurate, and a lick of flame follows every blow, searing the target in addition to the normal damage received. It is an efficient troll-killer, though it has not yet been heralded as such in song or legend.

