 6 Strength

Weight: 3~
@39462 = ~A sword of standardized enchantment, powerful though it is. The great southern nations are said to have once had legions of their soldiers armed in such a fashion, a force that must have appeared truly imposing on the battlefield. The days of such extravagance are long past though.

STATISTICS:

THAC0: +2
