 6 Strength

Weight: 4~
@39469 = ~This scimitar is of rather poor quality, but beneath its surface lies great power and evil. Created for the sole purpose of slaying Harpers, Shazzellim is more than capable of that task. With one strike of the blade, a Bard must make a Saving Throw vs. Spell or die. Crafted by a Red Wizard of Thay, the sword also has the ability to vocalize, which is why it was often given to fighter/mages in the service of the Wizards. Needless to say, possession of this sword would not be looked upon very highly by Harpers.

STATISTICS:

