Type: Two-handed

Weight: 3~
@39623 = ~~
@39624 = ~This humble staff radiates powerful magic, and was likely the simple-seeming weapon of a traveling mage or cleric. It would certainly prove more than ample for dealing with most threats encountered on the road. 

