 5 Strength

Weight: 3~
@39626 = ~Torm is said to manifest these items during times of great trouble, granting them to priests who care for the wounded, diseased, and poisoned. It is not to be taken for granted however, as the enchantment, though useful, is fleeting. It must be used with all due care.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Armor Class: +2

Charge abilities:
