 5 Strength

Weight: 3~
@39635 = ~This simple staff radiates a powerful enchantment, though its plain design suggests a simple origin. It reflects the quiet strength that faith brings, and was likely the modest weapon of a priest or cleric.

STATISTICS:

THAC0: +3
Damage: 1d6+3 (crushing)
