@40616 = ~This small mithral hammer is slightly warm to the touch. It is a symbol for Clan Battlehammer, a clan of dwarves currently led by the eighth king, Bruenor Battlehammer. The clan had always been led by his ancestors and passed on from generation to generation.

Originally, the clan resided in Mithral Hall, but when they were forced out, they moved to the northern regions of Icewind Dale. Near the Ten Towns, they set up a new home, providing equipment for the towns.

